%20highs%20around%206%2C300.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221906%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22s%26amp%3BP%20500%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a8709f748d8c055f5e3c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221056%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESmead%20Capital%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20rule%20that%20says%20the%20market's%20rally%20can't%20break%20higher%2C%20especially%20if%20economic%20fundamentals%2C%20like%20inflation%2C%20consumer%20spending%2C%20and%20the%20unemployment%20rate%2C%20remain%20solid.%20But%20to%20be%20sure%2C%20it's%20a%20foreboding%20reminder%20about%20how%20frothy%20the%20current%20environment%20is%2C%20and%20Smead%20thinks%20the%20market%20is%20set%20up%20for%20disaster%20where%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20delivers%20exceptionally%20poor%20returns%20over%20the%20decade%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20doesn't%20tell%20you%20when%2C%20but%20it%20does%20tell%20you%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20magnitude%20and%20the%20duration%20of%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Smead%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20hold%20your%20breath%20until%20it%20breaks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20question%20of%20whether%2C%20it's%20a%20question%20of%20when.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20market's%20impressive%20returns%20recently%20have%20been%20driven%20by%20growth%20stocks%2C%20particularly%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20mega-cap%20tech%20companies.%20So%20it's%20not%20necessarily%20surprising%20that%20Smead%2C%20a%20value%20investor%2C%20is%20bearish%20on%20growth%20stocks'%20prospects.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20shift%20toward%20value%20outperformance%20would%20benefit%20Smead's%20fund%2C%20which%20is%20down%2010.6%25%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months.%20The%20Smead%20Value%20Fund's%20holdings%20are%20most%20heavily%20concentrated%20in%20the%20energy%2C%20consumer%20cyclical%2C%20and%20financials%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Smead's%20impressive%20long-term%20track%20record%20shows%20he%20could%20be%20onto%20something.%20Other%20popular%20measures%20of%20investor%20euphoria%20also%20show%20the%20market%20is%20at%20historically%20rich%20levels.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Shiller%20cyclically-adjusted%20price-to-earnings%20ratio%20is%20near%20all-time%20highs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22s%26amp%3Bp%20500%20cape%20ratio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a8ffa85e81483682e4b4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22380%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGuruFocus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESmead%20also%20cited%20Warren%20Buffett's%20seemingly%20cautious%20approach%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20holding%20a%20record%20cash%20position%2C%20as%20a%20warning%20sign%20that%20things%20could%20go%20awry%20in%20the%20market.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-warren-buffett-dot-com-bubble-apple-smead-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBuffett%20warned%20of%20froth%20in%20the%20market%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leading%20him%20to%20take%20a%20more%20conservative%20stance%20in%20his%20portfolio.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20his%20performance%20suffered%20in%20the%20year%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20bubble's%20peak%2C%20but%20Buffett%20later%20smashed%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20returns%20when%20the%20market%20crashed%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221906%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22berkshire%20hathaway%20vs%20s%26amp%3Bp%20500%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a91d23d5881a51c1d9d46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22982%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESmead%20Capital%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20wants%20to%20know%20why%20Warren%20Buffe