ot%3BThe%20Apprentice%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202009%2C%20I%20was%20in%20a%20procurement%20meeting.%20One%20of%20the%20guys%20recognized%20me%20from%20the%20show.%20Then%2C%20another%20guy%20at%20the%20table%20looked%20at%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20you're%20not%20one%20of%20those%2C%20are%20you%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20cemented%20in%20my%20head%20that%20I%20probably%20shouldn't%20advertise%20that%20I%20was%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apprentice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20gone%20on%20the%20show%20hoping%20it%20would%20give%20me%20a%20leg%20up%20in%20my%20career.%20But%20I%20realized%20that%20if%20people%20had%20only%20heard%20of%20the%20show%20%E2%80%94%20not%20actually%20watched%20it%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20assume%20I%20was%20some%20narcissistic%20jerk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20nervous%20because%20I%20wanted%20a%20leg%20up%2C%20not%20the%20opposite%20of%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb43ddc7-8ece-42ad-b13c-8734ce01a218%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20I%20signed%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hadn't%20set%20out%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthen-and-now-reality-tv-stars-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebe%20on%20reality%20TV.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20economics%20at%20university%20and%20didn't%20do%20particularly%20well.%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20London%20and%20started%20looking%20for%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20lucky%20to%20get%20into%20telecoms%20at%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20millennium%20%E2%80%94%20it%20gave%20me%20a%20solid%20education%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20while%20working%20at%20TalkTalk%2C%20my%20boss%20asked%20if%20I'd%20ever%20watched%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apprentice.%26quot%3B%20He%20encouraged%20me%20to%20apply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20supercharge%20my%20career%20opportunities.%20It%20could%20be%20good%20exposure%20to%20potential%20employers%2C%20and%20perhaps%20I'd%20get%20spotted%20for%20sales-type%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20expect%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBill%20Gates%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20me%20head%20of%20sales%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20chance%20to%20demonstrate%20my%20rapport-building%20and%20sales%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221272%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22James%20McQuillan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a6dbc3d5881a51c1d9812%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221696%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJames%20McQuillan%20had%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20the%20producers%20were%20looking%20for.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20James%20McQuillan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20got%20to%20the%20interviews%2C%20I%20had%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20they%20were%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20lined%20you%20up%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNumber%20one%2C%20step%20forward.%26quot%3B%20The%20candidate%20would%20say%20their%20credentials%20%E2%80%94%20MBAs%20from%20Harvard%2C%20property%20portfolios%2C%20Cambridge%20degrees%2C%20and%20whatever%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20anything%20half%20as%20impressive%20to%20say%2C%20but%20I%20was%20watching%20the%20interview%20panel's%20reactions.%20That's%20when%20the%20penny%20dropped%3A%20they%20weren't%20looking%20for%20business%20acumen%20or%20academic%20brilliance.%20They%20were%20casting%20characters%20for%20a%20TV%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20sent%20through%20the%20door%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20were%20sent%20home.%20They%20were%20looking%20for%20someone%20with%20some%20business%20acumen%2C%20but%20more%20importantly%2C%20somebody%20the%20audience%20could%20engage%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20into%20it%20knowing%20it%20was%20heavily%20produced%20and%20all%20about%20the%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f34f4ce-9b87-4916-85f8-ea7a2449bef6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20came%20across%20as%20a%20bit%20goofy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apprentice%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20a%20straight%20business%20show%20%E2%80%94%20where%20people%20collaborated%2C%20had%20good%20ideas%2C%20and%20everything%20went%20smoothly%20%E2%80%94%20viewers%20would%20switch%20off.%20They%20needed%20stories%20and%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20it%20uncomfortable%20to%20play%20along%20%E2%80%94%20it%20wasn't%20sincere.%20But%20I%20was%20mindful%20this%20was%20a%20TV%20show%2C%20and%20if%20I%20didn't%20perform%2C%20I'd%20be%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20personal%20level%2C%20I%20was%20shy%20going%20into%20filming.%20When%20I%20had%20to%20give%20a%20speech%20at%20my%20wedding%2C%20I'd%20been%20nervous%20for%20months%20beforehand.%20Part%20of%20me%20thought%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apprentice%26quot%3B%20might%20help%20me%20get%20over%20that%2C%20which%20it%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20episodes%2C%20I%20came%20across%20as%20a%20bit%20goofy.%20I%20worried%20I'd%20damaged%20my%20career%20instead%20of%20accelerating%20it%2C%20and%20my%20wife%20was%20genuinely%20concerned%20I'd%20come%20across%20as%20unemployable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20I%20turned%20it%20around%20and%20ended%20up%20getting%20quite%20far%20in%20the%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221272%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22James%20McQuillan%20in%20an%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687a6d97f748d8c055f5e03e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221696%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJames%20McQuillan%20now%20works%20as%20a%20telecoms%20consultant.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20James%20McQuillan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20work%2C%20I%20was%20getting%20kudos.%20My%20colleagues%20were%20supportive%2C%20and%20clients%20who%20normally%20didn't%20answer%20were%20suddenly%20responding%20to%20my%20phone%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrangers%20didn't%20start%20reaching%20out%20until%20after%20the%20show%20aired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20mostly%20people%20asking%20me%20to%20invest%20in%20their%20businesses%2C%20which%20caught%20me%20off%20guard.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20needed%20money%20as%20much%20as%20they%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecruiters%20did%20get%20in%20touch%2C%20too%2C%20but%20I%20think%20they%20mostly%20just%20wanted%20to%20chat%20about%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22074e2bf6-2554-41ee-8576-37f8bcbda8c7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20thought%20it%20would%20leapfrog%20my%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apprentice%26quot%3B%20didn't%20derail%20my%20career%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20accelerate%20in%20the%20way%20I'd%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20I've%20followed%20the%20same%20path%20I%20would%20have%20if%20I%20hadn't%20done%20the%20show.%20I%20work%20in%20consulting.%20My%20previous%20role%20was%20as%20a%20managing%20director%20of%20Lycamobile%20for%20the%20UK%20and%20Ireland%20%E2%80%94%20a%20senior%20telecoms%20position%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20job%20people%20usually%20reach%20in%20their%20mid-40s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20applied%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apprentice%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20take%20me%20beyond%20that%2C%20but%20it%20never%20did.%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20get%20my%20earnings%20up%20very%20quickly%2C%20and%20that%20never%20manifested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20advertise%20having%20been%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apprentice%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20never%20put%20it%20on%20my%20CV%20or%20LinkedIn.%20I%20wasn't%20ashamed%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20bring%20it%20up%20during%20job%20applications%20in%20case%20it%20served%20as%20a%20disadvantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7e68461-3633-40c3-9e9c-a058d7967833%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20regret%20signing%20up%20for%20the%20show%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20regret%20doing%20the%20show.%20It%20catapulted%20me%20into%20new%20emotions%2C%20relationships%2C%20and%20exper