ffs%2C%20in%20Secaucus%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f729d6ffb6822ec6143df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222690%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESiddharth%20Cavale%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20landmark%20crypto%20bill%20that%20passed%20this%20week%20opens%20the%20door%20for%20more%20issuers%20to%20launch%20their%20own%20stablecoins.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20WSJ%20reported%20in%20June%20that%20retail%20Amazon%20and%20Walmart%20were%20looking%20into%20issuing%20their%20own%20coins.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20how%20it%20could%20work%20for%20businesses%20and%20their%20customers.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20landmark%20crypto%20bill%20that%20just%20passed%20in%20Congress%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20more%20businesses%20to%20issue%20their%20own%20stablecoins.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20corner%20of%20the%20crypto%20market%20has%20received%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20as%20the%20GENIUS%20Act%20moved%20toward%20becoming%20law%2C%20with%20crypto%20proponents%20cheering%20the%20huge%20show%20of%20legislative%20support.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20digital%20assets%20are%20a%20type%20of%20cryptocurrency%20pegged%20to%20fiat%20money%20like%20the%20US%20dollar.%20Right%20now%2C%20they're%20mostly%20used%20by%20crypto%20traders%20to%20easily%20buy%20other%20tokens.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20stablecoins%20used%20for%20payments%20would%20be%20a%20monumental%20shift%20in%20the%20foundations%20of%20commerce.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fwmt-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWalmart%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Famzn-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20considering%20launching%20their%20own%20stablecoins.%20Now%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenius-act-bitcoin-ethereum-price-stablecoins-coin-crcl-btc-eth-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20GENIUS%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20cleared%20the%20final%20legislative%20hurdle%2C%20crypto%20experts%20expect%20big%20changes%20to%20the%20payments%20ecosystem.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20to%20know.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c79a21e6-968a-44df-911d-b724f62c7d0f%5C%22%3EWhy%20would%20companies%20issue%20their%20own%20stablecoins%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20hard%20to%20see%20the%20incentive%20for%20big%20companies%20like%20Walmart%20or%20Amazon.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusinesses%20could%20save%20significant%20amounts%20in%20credit%20card%20processing%20fees%2C%20cutting%20out%20an%20expensive%20intermediary%20by%20having%20people%20use%20their%20proprietary%20crypto%20as%20payment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRetailers%20currently%20lose%20an%20estimated%202%25%20to%203%25%20of%20every%20transaction%20to%20credit%20card%20processing%20fees%2C%26quot%3B%20CoinRoutes%20co-founder%20%3Cbr%3EDave%20Weisberger%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20companies%20with%20billions%20in%20sales%2C%20eliminating%20even%20a%20portion%20of%20that%20margin%20drag%20could%20unlock%2010s%20of%20millions%20in%20savings.%20Stablecoins%20offer%20a%20potential%20alternative%20that%20reduces%20frictional%20costs%2C%20accelerates%20settlement%20times%2C%20and%20gives%20merchants%20more%20control%20over%20payment%20rails.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEliminating%20that%20type%20of%20cost%20would%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20Walmart%20and%20Amazon%2C%20but%20would%20be%20a%20blow%20to%20credit%20card%20issuers%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fv-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVisa%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fma-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMastercard%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20fraction%20of%20their%20customer%20base%20starts%20using%20a%20store-issued%20stablecoin%20instead%20of%20a%20Visa-backed%20card%2C%20that's%20billions%20in%20interchange%20fees%20gone%20overnight%2C%26quot%3B%20Will%20Reeves%2C%20CEO%20of%20bitcoin%20rewards%20app%20Fold%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisa%20recently%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20GENIUS%20Act%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20anticipated%20the%20market%20shift%20brought%20on%20by%20stablecoin%20adoption.%20It%20stated%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Blaying%20the%20groundwork%20by%20building%20and%20supporting%20blockchain-based%20solutions%20that%20help%20our%20partners%20and%20clients%20integrate%20stablecoins%20into%20the%20future%20of%20mainstream%20payments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22697849c2-b758-4160-b9ec-d0dcf1924ae8%5C%22%3EWhat%20will%20it%20mean%20for%20consumers%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20shopping%20with%20a%20retailer%20like%20Amazon%20or%20Walmart%2C%20a%20stablecoin%20payment%20system%20might%20not%20feel%20all%20that%20different%20from%20what%20they're%20doing%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kevin%20Lehtiniitty%2C%20CEO%20of%20stablecoin%20network%20Borderless.xyz%2C%20a%20stablecoin%20issued%20by%20a%20big%20retailer%20would%20feel%20similar%20to%20using%20a%20gift%20card.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReeves%20shared%20a%20similar%20perspective.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20surface%2C%20not%20much%20changes%20-%20you%20tap%20your%20phone%2C%20check%20out%2C%20maybe%20earn%20extra%20rewards%20or%20save%20on%20fees.%20But%20underneath%2C%20everything%20shifts.%20Walmart%20and%20Amazon%20aren't%20just%20retailers%20anymore%E2%80%94they're%20now%20your%20bank%20and%20your%20payment%20network.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benefit%20for%20shoppers%20could%20ultimately%20be%20lower%20prices%20if%20companies%20pass%20what%20they%20save%20in%20transaction%20fees%20to%20their%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompetition%20at%20this%20scale%20drives%20down%20transaction%20costs%2C%20and%20that%20means%20consumers%20will%20likely%20see%20lower%20prices%2C%20better%20rewards%2C%20or%20both%2C%26quot%3B%20Reeves%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDan%20Silverman%2C%20CEO%20of%20Balcony%20Technology%20Group%2C%20noted%20that%20the%20rise%20of%20corporate%20stablecoins%20could%20also%20prove%20beneficial%20to%20unbanked%20people%2C%20as%20it%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20access%20digital%20currency%20through%20their%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20thing%20I%20could%20also%20imagine%20is%20for%20loyalty%20points%20or%20rewards%20to%20be%20baked%20into%20the%20token%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%20%26quot%3BThink%20about%20when%20you%20get%20that%20long%20printed%20out%20receipt%20that%20has%20savings%20on%20it%20that%20you%20end%20up%20throwing%20out%20and%20never%20taking%20advantage%20of.%20The%20savings%20could%20be%20issued%20automatically%20on-chain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20for%20either%20company's%20stablecoin%20initiative%20to%20succeed%2C%20its%20customers%20would%20have%20to%20trust%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20potential%20downside%20for%20consumers%20is%20that%20stablecoins%20could%20add%20another%20layer%20to%20a%20process%20that's%20become%20pretty%20simple%20over%20the%20years.%20Shoppers%20would%20have%20to%20buy%20the%20stablecoins%20first%20and%20then%20use%20them%20to%20transact.%20For%20many%20people%2C%20it%20could%20be%20simpler%20to%20just%20keep%20using%20credit%20or%20debit%20cards%20already%20on%20file.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20risk%20for%20consumers%20is%20the%20management%20of%20stablecoin%20reserves.%20To%20hold%20their%20value%2C%20the%20tokens%20must%20be%20backed%20by%20an%20equivalent%20amount%20of%20liquid%20reserves%2C%20such%20as%20cash%20or%20short-term%20Treasurys.%20If%20these%20reserves%20are%20mismanaged%20or%20the%20issuing%20entity%20runs%20into%20financial%20trouble%2C%20the%20stablecoins%20could%20untether%20from%20their%20fiat%20